DESCRIPTION:**Day 2**\n- 07:30 🍳 Breakfast: Brown Bear — try their ve
 gan breakfast options\, ~₹200/person\n- 09:30 🏛️ Morning: Amber For
 t (open 08:00–18:00\, entry ₹250) — a stunning fort with a mix of Hi
 ndu and Mughal styles\, offering breathtaking views of the surrounding lan
 dscape\n  → Transport: Hire a shared jeep (₹800\, 45 minutes) for the 
 group\n- 13:00 🍽️ Lunch: 115 Cafe — recommended: their veggie burge
 rs\, ~₹350/person\n- 15:00 🎭 Afternoon: Jal Mahal (open 09:00–18:00
 \, entry free) — a beautiful water palace in the middle of Man Sagar Lak
 e\n  → Transport: Drive back to the city (30 minutes) and then take a sh
 ort walk to Jal Mahal\n- 19:00 🌅 Sunset: Hawa Mahal — admire the stun
 ning views of the city from this iconic palace\n- 20:00 🍷 Dinner: Govin
 dam Retreat — must-try: their vegan and gluten-free options\, ~₹400/pe
 rson\n- 💡 Local tip: Take a stroll through the nearby Kanwar Nagar mark
 et to experience the local culture\n- ☔ Indoor backup: Visit the Jaipur 
 Museum (open 10:00–17:30) to explore the city's history and art\n- 👥 
 Group tip: Consider booking a guided tour for the group to ensure a smooth
  and informative experience at Amber Fort
END:VEVENT
